item.title: Looking for talented coders!
item.dc:creator: @Ixl_Adds_Ixl Ixl Adds Ixl
item.description:
@Ixl_Adds_Ixl wrote:

[quote=“DePredaTe, post:3, topic:189346”]Sorry, I don’t think anyone knows you here. I would suggest giving us more details about the server, what it’s going to be, and what we are going to get for coding it. Maybe even telling us how it is going to be hosted. Telling us what you would need us to do, what coding you want done. Even telling us the source you are going to use. Do you have a website? Is it setup and ready to go? How far have you coded it so far? People don’t like looking at posts that are people who want a team, but don’t have any information.
When people don’t know information on project teams like this, they don’t bother. Sorry.[/quote]

Nice, i’ll add that to my thread “Tips on Maintaining a DEV Team”!
